and then went over to her, tapping her shoulder.<br>
<br>
&quot;Hey there! Glad to see you up. I've got an idea, hun. What do you say you and I take a trip back to Ephesus?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/usheyala.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sheyala</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 275<br> <font color=#993300>(8/27/01 9:50:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=180.topic&index=151>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Watcher</span><hr size=1> ::Shey listened to the strategies over and over, looking between Artemis her queen and her comrades.  These wars that took place in the amazon nations reminded her of her past, and each one hurt her heart to fight in.  But she fought none-the-less, but she was never sure wether it was for her. her sisters, or those she lost so long ago.  With a sigh she continued to listen, waiting for when they would move out and strike.  Silently she lie back against Anya (who was sleeping beside her) and took warmth from her fur:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 212<br> <font color=#993300>(8/27/01 12:54:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=180.topic&index=152>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Dawn, Delilah and Ari.</span><hr size=1> Alysia nodded to the guard saying she would speak with Delilah, but after hearing her words about Dawn's Tiger, she closed her eyes having a peaceful calm come over her as she turned to face Delilah and Dawn.<br>
<br>
&quot;Fear not sisters,&quot; She nodded. &quot;The Goddesses are already working on it.&quot;<br>
<br>
Though Alysia did not worship the Gods, few understood why she still respected them. She adored Athena and Artemis for years earlier, they had given her the immortal power to heal. After Alysia rejected her Goddess title, she still had a small connection with Athena.<br>
<br>
She turned and looked to Fogstone.<br>
<br>
&quot;You may place your men where you wish, I just hope that they do not give away the hiding places of my sisters.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udelilahtragedy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Delilah Tragedy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 43<br> <font color=#993300>(8/27/01 2:06:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=180.topic&index=153>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dawn, Delilah and Ari.</span><hr size=1> Delilah simply nodded, crossing her arms over her chest, her back and neck no longer hurting.  She watched Alysia while she spoke to the man, and continued to wait until Alysia was free to speak to her. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> X AmazonTears X</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(8/27/01 2:15:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=180.topic&index=154>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Crystal finally shows up</span><hr size=1> After days of tracking the Amazon troops, She finally comes to the camp. Crystal took longer then she would have but had left her horse behind to go on foot. That way she could hide and remain unseen. Quiet and careful, she wuddled up to the camp. About 5 months pregnate she didn`t mind war and the threat of being killed. She knew she could help out cooking and rending to the wounded.<br>
<br>
She moved quickly to her Latra, smiling &quot;Yasoo Ariah.&quot; She knew she was going to get yelled at but didn`t mind. &quot;I can`t really fight, but I can help out with other things. Just don`t send me back. My feet are killing me.&quot; Only 18, This was her first true war, she wanted to prove herself. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 213<br> <font color=#993300>(8/27/01 2:27:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=180.topic&index=155>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Delilah</span><hr size=1> Alysia nodded to Delilah seeing that she was no longer in pain. She silently thanked Athena for her help with the tiger and with the war as well.<br>
<br>
&quot;Delilah, I am free to speak with you now athelfi.&quot;<br>
<br>
She nodded to her athelfi and looked to the others.<br>
<br>
&quot;If you please, I wish for all except Dawn and Delilah to dismiss themselves.&quot;<br>
<br>
She nodded and once again watched the others leave her hut. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ulatraariah.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LaTra Ariah</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#993300>(8/27/01 2:33:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=180.topic&index=156>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Crystal finally shows up</span><hr size=1> She looked to Crystal and smiled slightly, happy to see one of her best friends. She glanced down to her stomach and quirked a brow, looking back up to her. &quot;You sure that baby'll be okay if you get your adrenaline up in a war?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udelilahtragedy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Delilah Tragedy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 44<br> <font color=#993300>(8/27/01 2:41:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=180.topic&index=157>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Delilah</span><hr size=1> She nodded to Alysia and waited for all the others to leave as she walked over to the map that the two Queens were looking over... Hmm.. she was right..<br>
<br>
Delilah glanced up at Alysia and Dawn and placed her hand on the map. &quot;I've been studying the weather a bit and it looks like the rain won't be letting up until far after the battle. I think we could use this to our advantage.&quot; glances up at them again, &quot;We are staying within familiar territories, yes?&quot;<br>
<br>
She quirked a brow and waited an answer. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 214<br> <font color=#993300>(8/27/01 3:20:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=180.topic&index=158>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Weather</span><hr size=1> She nodded looking over the map.<br>
<br>
&quot;I suppose we wont be traveling any further than 10 maybe 20 more miles west of here. And you're right, it could be held as an advantage.&quot;<br>
<br>
She looked over the map.<br>
<br>
&quot;If we stay in this area, I could send out a group to scout the area to make sure we know everything around us that we can.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udelilahtragedy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Delilah Tragedy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 45<br> <font color=#993300>(8/27/01 3:29:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=180.topic&index=159>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Weather</span><hr size=1> &quot;You may also want to be aware of this..&quot; she said an pointed to a very long, winding river about 10miles to the west. &quot;The rain has probably made it rough and alot wider than normal, AND I would expect there to be very deep parts in it too. We must be careful with that. Either we cross it or they cross it, but we should have some Amazons over there to check it out.&quot;<br>
<br>
She looked at the rest of the map, &quot;Anything else to be concerned about?&quot; <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udelilahtragedy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Delilah Tragedy</A> at: 8/27/01 3:32:36 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udawnithinia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dawnithinia </A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 310<br> <font color=#993300>(8/27/01 3:59:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=180.topic&index=160>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Listening. </span><hr size=1>  Dawn listened to Delilah as she spoke of her tiger, she didn't hold control over her specie, she just held their land, their home. <br>
<br>
 As she listened to Del and Alysia speak, she slowly drifted into Astral Projection. She would still be able to hear her sisters, and come back to reply. But things in Themiscrya had to be taken care of, she wasn't that big of a fuss, and things needed to be stopped.<br>
<br>
 She was getting very close to leaving Themiscrya. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uyoungevelyn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Young Evelyn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#993300>(8/27/01 4:12:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=180.topic&index=161>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/alteredsoulsx/images/evelyn-6.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Over to see Evelyn</span><hr size=1> Evelyn stops playing her flute as shes tapped on the shoulder.She looks up to see Ariah.&quot;Ariah!&quot;She hugs Ariah around the legs,looking up at her.She was all dirty from skipping around in the mud,and hugging Ariah got her dirty too.<br>
<br>
&quot;Okie,we can go on a trip.&quot;She nods,nods and nods a few more times,then lets Ariah go and shows her the flute Delilah gave her.&quot;See wha my friend gave me?&quot;She toots into the flute then giggles.<br>
<br>
She then noticed Crystal.&quot;Hi!!!!&quot;Waves her small hand to her. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Royal Fogstone</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(8/27/01 5:15:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=180.topic&index=162>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Disgusted...</span><hr size=1> ***Fogstone was a little disgusted by Alysia's response, for here over pridefulness of her amazons, and lack of care for her newly acquanted allies...Pride was usually not a problem, for he had much pride for the nation he was standing for. His warriors were no amatuars, at that matter, they were skilled hunters before they joined his army. It appeared in his mind that for a instant that the amazons were nothing but snobby little girls doing whatever they wanted, but oh well what are you going to do? Mutters:*** &quot;Amazons...&quot; *** And gives a grin to himself as he walked out of the tent, making his own little plan in his head about what part he was going to take in this war... Or even if it wasn't even joining the amazons iin war... Maybe, fighting agenst the amazons to show them a glimps of reality that they wearen;t so invincible...***   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=sartha>Sartha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 168<br> <font color=#993300>(8/27/01 5:18:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=180.topic&index=163>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Dawn</span><hr size=1> ::Sartha had been left to dwell in the shadows as the waiting had continued, but now she ventured inside, having been aware of Dawn's presence for awhile. She glanced to Alysia, Delilah, and the others and nodded to them all out of respect, then looked to Dawn as she was laid out in her suspended state while she used her projection. A moment later, she kneeled beside her Athelfi, bowed her head, and closed her eyes. She would wait for Dawn to return:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> X Amazontears X</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(8/27/01 9:04:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=180.topic&index=164>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Saying her Yasoos</span><hr size=1> She smiled to the little girl. &quot;Yasoo little one, how are you ?&quot;<br>
<br>
After talking to the little one for a moment, Crystal went to each Amazon Queen and gave each a respectful greeting. When that was done she seat down and pulled some cloth from her large pack. One by one, she counted them and rolled them. They will be used to rap the wounds for the injuried. In alittle bit she`ll try to gather some straight sticks for splints.<br>
